# Wizard Menu Library

Reusable menu templates for consistent wizard experience.

## Menu Components

MenuOption {
  number: 1..9
  icon: emoji
  label: string
  description?: string // shown in beginner mode
  example?: string
  recommended?: boolean
}

Menu {
  id: string
  title: string
  context?: string
  options: [MenuOption]
  recommendation?: string
  helpText?: string
  nextMenu: (choice) => MenuId
}

